how do you make the sloppy bun if you have curly hair i have curly hair and i make a cute sloppy bun all the time first of all make sure your hair isn't frizzy cause that is when it looks bad deep condition your hair and when you are out of the shower don't rub your hair with a towel because this causes frizz also try using a frizz ease serum like the one in the so sexy line by victoria secret flip your head over and gather all your hair up in a big pile then twist a hair tie around it you can retry if it looks bad or pull certain sections to make it look better another idea i prefer is pulling it all back while standing up then taking butterfly clips and clipping it all back it looks super cute and prevent it from looking like something you threw together at the last second hope this helped and good luck Haircut Professional wrestling throws Three Stooges Shampoo Suplex Aerial (dance move) Knife Great Teacher Onizuka Dreadlocks Professional wrestling holds The Ashlee Simpson Show Pittsburgh Steelers Textile manufacturing Physical attractiveness Phoebe Buffay's songs Equine conformation Depilation Shawn Michaels Mattress Powerbomb Big Brother (USA TV series) Kodocha Shaving Hip hop collaborations Yu-Gi-Oh! Trading Card Game Veruca Salt Professional wrestling aerial techniques Cleveland Browns Professional wrestling double-team maneuvers Fruits Basket Ponytail Late Night with Conan O'Brien Social rule Bish__jo game New York Giants Characters in the Smurfs Ron and Fez Futurama (TV series - season 3) The Life and Times of Juniper Lee Poker jargon Teen Girl Squad Dil Pickles Super Bowl XIV Humphrey Bogart Mnemonic Baldness Happy Tree Friends Professional wrestling attacks Pubic hair Lisa the Vegetarian Diving Jim Bunning Jerry Coleman Drill bit Skateboarding trick Dilbert Nathan's Hot Dog Eating Contest Poodle Chibiusa Bangladeshi cricket team in Sri Lanka in 2005-06 Coin flipping Neckbreaker Mixed martial arts Backstroke The Star Wars Holiday Special Pitaten Profession